reviewText: My toddler cannot stop singing this songs.
My twins love the Galinha Pintadinha videos so much that I decided to buy the #1 and 2 trilingual videos for their day care. All the kids loved the videos and have fun watching / dancing / singing.
Delivery was SUPER fast and the wrapping paper that came with it was superrrrr cute!!! The DVD is great, I love the songs and my daughter loved it!! Happy baby, Happy mama.
Arrived fast, love the bag, ordering a second DVD.
Arrived very fast. I love the lottie dottie wrapping paper that the dvd's came in. Very cute.
